parameters.name: Mg_CountRate_ChanD_avg
parameters.description: ---> Mg count rate channel D (Ions2). This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function spdf_3d_to_2d_avg_over_col (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['Mg_CountRate_ChanD'].
